 131:../../../PY32F002B_Firmware_V1.2.1/PY32F002B_Firmware_V1.2.1/Drivers/PY32F002B_HAL_Driver/Src/py32f002b_hal.c ****        (++) functions affecting time base configurations are declared as __weak
